cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for detecting and removing shadows from images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves segmentation, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of reflectance and illumination characteristics suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
